ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Definitely - great combination of theory, reality, and field trips.
I absolutely would recommend the course to fellow students, particularly those who are interested in IR theory, as we devoted a significant amount of time to their application in an Iranian context.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course developed my rather underdeveloped knowledge of Iran as a key region in the Middle East. As such it has been very helpful in deepening my knowledge of the ME, IR theory, and my overall MA degree.
